OL,7,FAround 130 homes are being evacuated
OL,8,Fwithin a 100m cordon surrounding a
OL,9,Fproperty in Grimethorpe.
OL,11,FThe cordon was put in place earlier
OL,12,Ftoday (8 May) after police found
OL,13,F'suspicious items' whilst executing a
OL,14,Fwarrant at an address on Brierley Road.
OL,16,FThe Army bomb squad were called in and
OL,17,Fa number of fire engines are also at
OL,18,Fthe scene while emergency services
OL,19,Fcontinue their investigation.
