OL,7,FA 58-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of firearms offences and
OL,9,Fremains in custody.
OL,11,FThose residents affected have been
OL,12,Fadvised they may be out of their homes
OL,13,Ffor 48 hours and are asked to pack a
OL,14,Fbag with all the essentials they may
OL,15,Fneed for the next couple of days -
OL,16,Fgiving consideration to any medication
OL,17,Fand also their pets.
