OL,7,FBarnsley Council has opened a rest
OL,8,Fcentre at St Luke's Church for
OL,9,Fresidents who don't have anywhere else
OL,10,Fto go during the evacuation.
OL,12,FThere are no schools within the cordon
OL,13,Fand pupils at Milefield Primary,
OL,14,FLadywood Primary and Outwood Academy
OL,15,Fcan be collected at usual at pick-up
OL,16,Ftime. Parents have been contacted
OL,17,Fdirectly about further arrangements.
OL,19,FEmergency services, the army's
OL,20,FExplosive Ordnance Disposal (EOD) team
OL,21,Fand other partners remain in the area.
