OL,7,FAll roads within the 100m cordon are
OL,8,Fclosed and members of the public are
OL,9,Fasked to avoid the area.
OL,11,FAssistant Chief Constable David
OL,12,FHartley, gold commander, said: "We are
OL,13,Fvery grateful to local residents for
OL,14,Ftheir continued patience and
OL,15,Funderstanding as we carry out our
OL,16,Fvital work.
OL,18,F"This has already greatly helped our
OL,19,Fresponse and public safety will remain
OL,20,Fat the forefront of our minds as this
OL,21,Finvestigation progresses."
