OL,7,FCoun Sir Steve Houghton CBE, Leader of
OL,8,FBarnsley Council, said: "We're working
OL,9,Fclosely with our colleagues at South
OL,10,FYorkshire Police, and we have staff
OL,11,Fout in the area supporting their
OL,12,Fresponse.
OL,14,F"We have opened a rest centre at St
OL,15,FLuke's Church for people who are being
OL,16,Fevacuated and don't have anywhere else
OL,17,Fto go. I urge local people to follow
OL,18,Fthe advice from the police and keep
OL,19,Fthem and their families safe."
